<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_66_r2l20"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Münıch von <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l21"> <expan>Amptman<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſvorheım </del> Sünſʒheim </ab>
</div>
