<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_66_r2l22"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe ewch Berlin Pfob von ſünſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l23">heim geſagt hab daʒ Jm ein pferd bey vns ʒu <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſölt ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l24">etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> ıſt vns von den dıngen / ee </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l25">vns eẅr brıef ward niht wıſſenlıch <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> Auf das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l26">vns beſant / ſölıch dıe der ſache ʒu ſchıken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> mıt Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l27"><expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt . dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ ſıe dıe ſache niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l28">handelt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn als des Reıchs gerıchts form vnd <expan>gewonh<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l29">vns ſey / VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır doch / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedıgen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l30">Otten ʒu dıenſt vnd <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu lıeb . <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mıt Jn geredt / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l31">ſıe dauon <expan>gelaſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd dem <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> der vns <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> bracht hat . Das </ab>
