<add><ab facs="#facs_66_r1l1"><expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan> </ab></add> pferd <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Otten <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l35"><expan>gedıene<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd 
